item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Tax_Rates
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Tax_Rates Datatype Description This contains the four tax rates, one for each fee type. Local laborTaxRate The tax rate associated with the labor fee. Type: decimal locationId A reference to a location. Type: decimal oneTimeTaxRate The tax rate associated with the one-time fee. Type: decimal recurringTaxRate The tax rate associated with the recurring fee. Type: decimal
